      "tanglishNotes": "Indha waveguide-oda, frequency 6.56 GHz ku mela signal poga mudiyum. Rectangular pipe madiri irukum. Aprm, phase velocity-um group velocity-um different dhan. Namma calculate pannina: fc = c/(2a) nu formula use pannanum."
